node.text:
Have you heard about the Shelf Clouds seen earlier this week in Georgia? ☁️

Shelf and roll clouds are types of arcus clouds, and are known to have the shape of a long bar or shelf below a storm cloud. Have you ever seen them before?

Video by Jaymi Knight
